data.description: Charming, well maintained 3-bed, 1-bath home with new carpet, garage doors, light fixtures, and fresh paint inside and outside! More improvements this property features are solar panels, new windows both w/ lifetime warranty, front yard sprinkler system, Nest thermostat, water softener, RO system, security system, and new motor outside AC unit (1yr). Electric bill is approx. $300-$400 A YEAR - per seller. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
